<HI>Charge,</HI> His Friendship
keepes pace with ours.
If thou doest well, shalt
thou not bee accepted?
(sayes Hee to <HI>Cain</HI>) doe
well, and have well, such
as wee behave our selves
<PB N="53" REF="30">
