when the one is sad the o|ther
is trobled, there is no
Amity where there is no
<PB N="54" REF="31">
Sympathy; If I doe not
suffer in my SAVIOVR,
I doe not love Him. Can
the Head be ficke and the
Body not feele it.</P>
<P>There is a time to
