of whom wee live and
moove: 'Tis all hee re|quires,
an egge of his
owne <HI>Bird,</HI> some minutes
of that time which hee
hath given us. What can
I doe lesse? one good
<PB N="137" REF="72">
turne requires another,
if I love not those that
love mee, I come short
