<HI>Christians:</HI> hee that will
not be in charity shall ne|ver
be in heaven. Why
should I doe my selfe a
shrewd turne because a|nother
<PB N="151" REF="79">
would?</P>
<P>It was the divell that
first made us enemies to
<HI>God,</HI> and it is still he that
